The '''International Conference on Systems Biology''' is the primary [[international]] [[Academic conference|conference]] for [[systems biology]] [[research]]. Created by [[Hiroaki Kitano]] in 2000, its organization is now coordinated by the [http://www.issb.org/ International Society for Systems Biology] (ISSB).
